reviews.review_text: Deal......whole 2nd set Download before you finish reading this sentence....raunchy Scarlet to start an eclectic 2nd set.  Touch closer...Playin'> MD......mmmmm..... and what a fine night it was....props to Jimmy Ward for a fabulous  weekend in the woods!!

This for 1st Set, 143267 or 154660 of Set 2 Since the versions coming from the Silberman source are all only Set 2, and are clearly the only choice, we still need part 1. I'd say this is clearly the current front runner.

WHEN OH WHEN WILL DAVE PAY SOMEONE FOR A CLUE? SBD OF 6/18/83, REMASTERED...SI HUNTER CAN MATRIX THAT SHIT UP...IT IS A COLLECTIVE COSMIC WET DREAM AT THIS POINT MAN. STOP RELEASING SHIOWS WE ALREADY HAVE KILLER SOURCES FOR PLEASE. 

Fwiw, this is a 50 star show. Rowdiest Scarlet ever, no debate, not even close. Dew, well for many this is also a no debate version. I'll say there a less than a handful that dance on top of the mountain, and this is one. Loads of other highlights though.

Sounds good but a lot of problems during Fire on the Mountain Set 1 sounds good but Fire on the Mountain has a lot of flutter issues that aren't noted in the info source.  Seek another source for Set 2.
